ity, the authors conclude, politicians articulate society's dreams and bureaucrats bring them gingerly to earth.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Apr 2021) 0aGovernment executivesxEurope. 0aGovernment executivesxUnited States. 0aHauts fonctionnairesxEurope. 0aHauts fonctionnairesxÉtats-Unis. 0aHommes politiquesxEurope. 0aHommes politiquesxÉtats-UnisxEuropexUnited States. 0aPoliticiansxEurope. 0aPoliticiansxUnited States. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aPutnam, Robert D., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRockman, Bert A., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z978311044221240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674020047423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780674020047.jpg  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1896-2004c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK